    <item>
  <title>Bahrain 6 March 2026 #1</title>
  <link>https://www.crisisgroup.org/content/bahrain-6-march-2026-1</link>
  <description>
&lt;span&gt;Bahrain 6 March 2026 #1&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;nrafati&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T22:23:08+01:00" title="Friday, March 6, 2026 - 22:23"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 22:23&lt;/time&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;a href="https://www.crisisgroup.org/bahrain" hreflang="en"&gt;Bahrain&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;div class="paragraph paragraph--type--timeline-date paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
            &lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T12:00:00Z"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 12:00&lt;/time&gt;

  6 March 2026
  &lt;p&gt;CENTCOM &lt;a href="https://x.com/CENTCOM/status/2029960748542071300" target="_blank"&gt;noted&lt;/a&gt; that “last night, Iranian forces fired seven attack drones at civilian, residential neighbourhoods in Bahrain”.&lt;/p&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;

</description>
  <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 21:23:08 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator>nrafati</dc:creator>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">27449 at https://www.crisisgroup.org</guid>
    </item>
<item>
  <title>Iraq 6 March 2026 #1</title>
  <link>https://www.crisisgroup.org/content/iraq-6-march-2026-1</link>
  <description>
&lt;span&gt;Iraq 6 March 2026 #1&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;nrafati&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T22:22:28+01:00" title="Friday, March 6, 2026 - 22:22"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 22:22&lt;/time&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;a href="https://www.crisisgroup.org/iraq" hreflang="en"&gt;Iraq&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;div class="paragraph paragraph--type--timeline-date paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
            &lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T12:00:00Z"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 12:00&lt;/time&gt;

  6 March 2026
  &lt;p&gt;The U.S. Embassy in Baghdad &lt;a href="https://x.com/USEmbBaghdad/status/2029984683639845340" target="_blank"&gt;warned&lt;/a&gt; that “Iran-aligned terrorist militias may seek to target hotels frequented by foreigners in the Kurdistan Region of Iraq”.&lt;/p&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;

</description>
  <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 21:22:28 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator>nrafati</dc:creator>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">27448 at https://www.crisisgroup.org</guid>
    </item>
<item>
  <title>Washington 6 March 2026 #1</title>
  <link>https://www.crisisgroup.org/content/washington-6-march-2026-1</link>
  <description>
&lt;span&gt;Washington 6 March 2026 #1&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;nrafati&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T22:22:00+01:00" title="Friday, March 6, 2026 - 22:22"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 22:22&lt;/time&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;a href="https://www.crisisgroup.org/washington" hreflang="en"&gt;Washington&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;div class="paragraph paragraph--type--timeline-date paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
            &lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T12:00:00Z"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 12:00&lt;/time&gt;

  6 March 2026
  &lt;p&gt;President Pezeshkian &lt;a href="https://x.com/drpezeshkian/status/2029877231942590545" target="_blank"&gt;stated&lt;/a&gt;: “Some countries have begun mediation efforts. Let's be clear: we are committed to lasting peace in the region yet we have no hesitation in defending our nation's dignity and sovereignty. Mediation should address those who underestimated the Iranian people and ignited this conflict”. Meanwhile, President Trump &lt;a href="https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/116182551337254643" target="_blank"&gt;declared&lt;/a&gt; that “there will be no deal with Iran except unconditional surrender! After that, and the selection of a great and acceptable leader(s), we, and many of our wonderful and very brave allies and partners, will work tirelessly to bring Iran back from the brink of destruction, making it economically bigger, better and stronger than before”. Trump later &lt;a href="https://www.axios.com/2026/03/06/trump-iran-war-unconditional-surrender" target="_blank"&gt;indicated&lt;/a&gt; that “unconditional surrender could be that [the Iranians] announce it. But it could also be when they can’t fight any longer because they don’t have anyone or anything to fight with”.&lt;/p&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;

</description>
  <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 21:22:00 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator>nrafati</dc:creator>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">27447 at https://www.crisisgroup.org</guid>
    </item>
<item>
  <title>Tehran 6 March 2026 #1</title>
  <link>https://www.crisisgroup.org/content/tehran-6-march-2026-1</link>
  <description>
&lt;span&gt;Tehran 6 March 2026 #1&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;nrafati&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T22:19:21+01:00" title="Friday, March 6, 2026 - 22:19"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 22:19&lt;/time&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;a href="https://www.crisisgroup.org/tehran" hreflang="en"&gt;Tehran&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;div class="paragraph paragraph--type--timeline-date paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
            &lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T12:00:00Z"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 12:00&lt;/time&gt;

  6 March 2026
  &lt;p&gt;President Pezeshkian &lt;a href="https://x.com/drpezeshkian/status/2029877231942590545" target="_blank"&gt;stated&lt;/a&gt;: “Some countries have begun mediation efforts. Let's be clear: we are committed to lasting peace in the region yet we have no hesitation in defending our nation's dignity and sovereignty. Mediation should address those who underestimated the Iranian people and ignited this conflict”. Meanwhile, President Trump &lt;a href="https://truthsocial.com/@realDonaldTrump/posts/116182551337254643" target="_blank"&gt;declared&lt;/a&gt; that “there will be no deal with Iran except unconditional surrender! After that, and the selection of a great and acceptable leader(s), we, and many of our wonderful and very brave allies and partners, will work tirelessly to bring Iran back from the brink of destruction, making it economically bigger, better and stronger than before”. Trump later &lt;a href="https://www.axios.com/2026/03/06/trump-iran-war-unconditional-surrender" target="_blank"&gt;indicated&lt;/a&gt; that “unconditional surrender could be that [the Iranians] announce it. But it could also be when they can’t fight any longer because they don’t have anyone or anything to fight with”.&lt;/p&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;

</description>
  <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 21:19:21 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator>nrafati</dc:creator>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">27446 at https://www.crisisgroup.org</guid>
    </item>
<item>
  <title>Lebanon 6 March 2026 #1</title>
  <link>https://www.crisisgroup.org/content/lebanon-6-march-2026-1</link>
  <description>
&lt;span&gt;Lebanon 6 March 2026 #1&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;nrafati&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T22:18:56+01:00" title="Friday, March 6, 2026 - 22:18"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 22:18&lt;/time&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;a href="https://www.crisisgroup.org/lebanon" hreflang="en"&gt;Lebanon&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;div class="paragraph paragraph--type--timeline-date paragraph--view-mode--default"&gt;
            &lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T12:00:00Z"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 12:00&lt;/time&gt;

  6 March 2026
  &lt;p&gt;The Israeli military &lt;a href="https://x.com/IDF/status/2029803151759446071" target="_blank"&gt;conducted&lt;/a&gt; what it described as “a broad-scale wave of 26 strikes in the Dahieh area of Lebanon, targeting Hizbollah infrastructure. Among the targets were an executive council’s command center and a facility storing UAVs used for attacks against Israel”. The IDF same day &lt;a href="https://x.com/IDF/status/2029934460003602485" target="_blank"&gt;reported&lt;/a&gt; that eight of its soldiers were injured “as a result of projectile fire toward Israel near the Lebanese border”, while Lebanese &lt;a href="https://english.alarabiya.net/News/middle-east/2026/03/06/lebanon-says-217-killed-798-wounded-in-israeli-strikes-since-monday" target="_blank"&gt;authorities&lt;/a&gt; reported more than 200 fatalities and nearly 800 injuries since 2 March. The IDF’s chief of staff &lt;a href="https://www.timesofisrael.com/liveblog_entry/idf-chief-says-israel-to-seize-every-opportunity-to-strike-hezbollah/" target="_blank"&gt;remarked&lt;/a&gt;: “We are crushing the Iranian terror regime and will seize every opportunity to deepen our achievements. Hizbollah chose to join the campaign alongside Iran and is paying the price… We will not give up on disarming Hizbollah”.&lt;/p&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;

</description>
  <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 21:18:56 +0000</pubDate>
    <dc:creator>nrafati</dc:creator>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">27445 at https://www.crisisgroup.org</guid>
    </item>
<item>
