        &lt;h1 class="c-page-hero__title [ u-fs36 u-fs50@l u-lh1 u-wbbw ]" dir="ltr" lang="en"&gt;
      A Sprawling Middle East War Explodes
    &lt;/h1&gt;&lt;!-- /.c-page-hero__title --&gt;

    
          &lt;div class="c-page-hero__teaser [ u-ptserif u-fs18 u-fs15@m u-fs18@l u-fsi ]" dir="ltr" lang="en"&gt;
        &lt;div class="word-wrap"&gt;&lt;p&gt;A joint U.S.-Israeli attack on Iran, followed by Iranian retaliation against U.S. military assets, Israel and other U.S. allies, has engulfed much of the Middle East in conflict. Crisis Group experts offer a 360-degree view of the new war’s initial reverberations in the region.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /.c-page-hero__teaser --&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /.c-page-hero__details --&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /.c-page-hero --&gt;
                      
