<item>
  <title>Operation Epic Folly? Trump’s and Netanyahu’s War on Iran</title>
  <link>https://www.crisisgroup.org/pod/middle-east-north-africa/iran/operation-epic-folly-trumps-and-netanyahus-war-iran</link>
  <description>
&lt;span&gt;Operation Epic Folly? Trump’s and Netanyahu’s War on Iran&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;hschaub&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span&gt;&lt;time datetime="2026-03-06T19:00:43+01:00" title="Friday, March 6, 2026 - 19:00"&gt;Fri, 03/06/2026 - 19:00&lt;/time&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;div class="s-wrapper u-display-flex u-bg-white u-z-1"&gt;
    &lt;aside class="js-side-nav c-side-nav"&gt;

  &lt;ul class="o-list o-list--vertical c-side-nav__list u-ls-025"&gt;
    &lt;li class="c-side-nav__list__item"&gt;
      &lt;a href="https://www.crisisgroup.org/latest-updates" class="u-ttu"&gt;Latest Updates&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;/ul&gt;

        &lt;ul class="o-list o-list--vertical c-side-nav__list u-ls-025"&gt;
                                      &lt;li class="c-side-nav__list__item"&gt;
            &lt;a href="javascript:;" class="u-ttu js-side-nav__item" data-target="subregion-africa" data-depth="2"&gt;Africa&lt;span class="o-icon o-icon--xxs"&gt;&lt;svg&gt;&lt;use xlink:href="#chevron-right" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" /&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
          &lt;/li&gt;
                                &lt;li class="c-side-nav__list__item"&gt;
            &lt;a href="javascript:;" class="u-ttu js-side-nav__item" data-target="subregion-asia-pacific" data-depth="2"&gt;Asia-Pacific&lt;span class="o-icon o-icon--xxs"&gt;&lt;svg&gt;&lt;use xlink:href="#chevron-right" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" /&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
