        &lt;h1 class="c-page-hero__title [ u-fs36 u-fs50@l u-lh1 u-wbbw ]" dir="ltr" lang="en"&gt;
      Operation Epic Folly? Trump’s and Netanyahu’s War on Iran
    &lt;/h1&gt;&lt;!-- /.c-page-hero__title --&gt;

    
          &lt;div class="c-page-hero__teaser [ u-ptserif u-fs18 u-fs15@m u-fs18@l u-fsi ]" dir="ltr" lang="en"&gt;
        &lt;div class="word-wrap"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This week on &lt;em&gt;Hold Your Fire!&lt;/em&gt;, Richard talks with Crisis Group experts Ali Vaez, Yasmine Farouk, Mairav Zonszein and Michael Wahid Hanna about the U.S.-Israel war with Iran, its fallout in the Gulf and wider region and what might come next.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /.c-page-hero__teaser --&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /.c-page-hero__details --&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- /.c-page-hero --&gt;
                      
