                  &lt;a href="https://www.crisisgroup.org/es/qna/latin-america-caribbean/venezuela/us-snaps-venezuelas-oil-and-rare-minerals-race-supplies" class="[ u-df u-jcfs u-aic u-width-100 ] [ u-pad-l15 u-pad-r15 u-pad-t15 u-pad-b15 ]"&gt;
